%!PS-Adobe-3.0 EPSF-3.0
%%BoundingBox: 0 0 100 100
%% Set disk0 root to /tmp then use pipe through disk device
systemdict /SystemParamsPassword () put
<< /Root (/tmp) >> currentsystemparams /GenericResourceDir get
(%disk0%) .putdevparams
(%disk0%pipe_test) (w) file (test) writestring closefile
showpage
